main event: On November 8, 1964, a military report described a probable meteor observation characterized by a flaming green object that broke up and burned for three seconds.
interesting points: The object was observed to move west to east,The duration of the flaming object was very brief at three seconds,There were no confirmed witnesses listed in the report,The report was part of Project Blue Book, which focused on UFO sightings,The document was sent to various military and intelligence agencies, indicating the importance of the sighting.
